    • Method Detail

      • parseVersion

        int parseVersion()
        Returns the parse version associated with this SPI. The parse version should be an unsigned 16-bit value. The parse version should be incremented every time the service provider implementation is modified to produce different results.

        Version number 0 is reserved and should never be returned by this method.

        Returns:
        The 16-bit unsigned parse version
